single spawn mobs should be 1 of 2 things, FCFS (first come first serve) or rotation... FCFS is usually great for a single guild when the spawn time is in their prime playing, and usually results in pretty much a monopoly of the spawn due to this fact. a rotation spreads the wealth to whole server.<br>
